    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/response-to-daily-mail-claims-about-the-green-belt"/>
    <title>Response to Daily Mail claims about the green belt</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Communities Minister Andrew Stunell said:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;The Green Belt provides an important protection against urban sprawl, providing a ‘green lung’ around towns and cities. The Coalition Agreement commits the Government to safeguarding Green Belt and other environmental designations, which they have been in the new National Planning Policy Framework.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
